{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636890/extras/ColdVR_Score_Card.png?t=1739441282\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep moving.\u00a0\u00a0 You\u2019ve got to keep moving.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Because in the high adrenaline shooter Cold VR, when you slow down, time goes faster, and so does the relentless enemy AI.\u00a0\u00a0 And you really don\u2019t want that to happen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636890/extras/A_Wolf_In_VR_Quote.png?t=1739441282\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636890/extras/VR_Realm_Quote_Image.png?t=1739441282\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">COLD VR is an exhilarating virtual reality game that puts you in control of time.\u00a0\u00a0 Stay on the move to outwit and outmanoeuvre the relentless enemy AI. The fate of the virtual world rests in your hands! Time is your greatest weapon. Move to slow it down, stop, and risk everything.\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Designed for those who crave a challenge and love the rush of adrenaline. As you progress through the chillingly beautiful environments, you'll face not only numerous, more powerful enemies, including those in the scary Backrooms levels, but also environmental hazards such as deadly lasers, moving platforms, and unexpected surprises for those daring enough to explore.\u00a0 With its twisting mechanics, this game will turn you into an unstoppable machine as you adapt and overcome challenges in each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636890/extras/tech_radar_quotes.png?t=1739441282\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636890/extras/game_or_die_quote.png?t=1739441282\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 40 levels including the feared backroom levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the shoes of the protagonist in a unique blend of live-action and in-game storytelling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your choices will determine humanity's fate.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2636890?t=1739441282","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636890/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739441282","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636890/d481523238e9c17c695e6adff84349d8e4c36e21/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739441282","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636890/d481523238e9c17c695e6adff84349d8e4c36e21/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739441282","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"VR Only","id":54},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2921450,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636890/extras/ColdVR_Score_Card.png?t=1739441282\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep moving.\u00a0\u00a0 You\u2019ve got to keep moving.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Because in the high adrenaline shooter Cold VR, when you slow down, time goes faster, and so does the relentless enemy AI.\u00a0\u00a0 And you really don\u2019t want that to happen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636890/extras/A_Wolf_In_VR_Quote.png?t=1739441282\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636890/extras/V